01:22:43,932 --> 01:22:45,832
Thorntone, razmisli.

1421
01:22:45,867 --> 01:22:47,698
Šta se to zbiva?

1422
01:22:49,104 --> 01:22:52,562
Philipe, oladi. Moj je red.

1423
