Doug Nelson.

1449
01:24:23,798 --> 01:24:26,323
Znaš što se gotovo nikad ne vidi?

1450
01:24:26,368 --> 01:24:29,496
Kad neko pokušava sjebat skakača.

1451
01:24:42,150 --> 01:24:45,142
- Dobar si ti mali.
- Hvala Lou.

1452
01:24:45,187 --> 01:24:49,851
Moli, suzdržite se
od glasnih zvukova za vrijem skokova.

1453
01:24:52,027 --> 01:24:55,929
Slijedi, za Atlantic
Eastern Eaglese,

1454
01:24:55,964 --> 01:24:57,989
Bill Steincap.

1455
01:25:16,484 --> 01:25:20,477
Time završavaju 10m visinski
skokovi Atlantic Easterna.

1456
01:25:20,522 --> 01:25:23,320
Slijede, Grand Lakes Hooters.

1457
01:25:26,261 --> 01:25:27,888
Samo da vas podsjetimo,

1458
01:25:27,929 --> 01:25:30,193
karte za sva sportska
natjecanja Grand Lakesa,

1459
01:25:30,232 --> 01:25:33,292
dostupna su u
studentskim uredima.

1460
01:25:33,335 --> 01:25:35,428
Zanima te Valerie Desmond?

1461
01:25:35,470 --> 01:25:38,064
Ona je sa mnom.

1462
01:25:38,106 --> 01:25:40,836
Dolaziš na svoje, ha Melone?

1463
01:25:40,875 --> 01:25:42,342
Ja si nebi lomio ruke,

1464
01:25:42,377 --> 01:25:44,607
češkajući si leža da sam
na tvome mjestu.

1465
01:25:44,646 --> 01:25:46,637
Zato jer, zapamti ovo,
slagaču ručnika..

1466
01:25:46,681 --> 01:25:49,809
što god misliš o sebi,
uvijek ćeš biti grbav,

1467
01:25:49,851 --> 01:25:52,479
odvratan, i bogati plačljivac.

1468
01:25:52,520 --> 01:25:54,852
I završit ćeš baš kao svoj otac.

1469
01:25:54,889 --> 01:25:58,848
Bože, nadam se, jer ga volim.

1470
01:25:58,893 --> 01:26:02,192
Prvi za Grand Lakes sveučilište skače..

1471
01:26:02,230 --> 01:26:04,357
Chas Osbourne.

1472
01:26:04,399 --> 01:26:07,129
Nedavni nacionalni prvak.

1473
01:26:34,429 --> 01:26:37,421
- Jason jesi skakao?
- Ne. Jesi prošao?

1474
01:26:37,465 --> 01:26:38,932
Nemam pojma. Javit će mi.

