Trostruki Lindy.

1506
01:29:14,722 --> 01:29:17,282
- Jel to teško?
- Nemoguće.

1507
01:30:40,842 --> 01:30:43,333
Melon! Uspio si!

1508
01:30:48,249 --> 01:30:49,614
Bilo je super!

1509
01:30:54,255 --> 01:30:58,214
Ajme, bio si strašan!
To je bilo nevjerojatno!

1510
01:30:58,259 --> 01:31:00,727
Vjerojatno ne postoji
nešto što ne možeš.

1511
01:31:00,762 --> 01:31:02,923
Imam ti rezultate ispita.

1512
01:31:02,964 --> 01:31:04,090
